    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes a perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door\u2014typical of a well-loved car that has seen regular road use. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather upholstery; while the driver\u2019s bolster shows light natural creasing, the interior remains free of any tears, odors, or unsightly stains. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented history of on-time oil changes and fluid flushes. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires have roughly 75% tread remaining, and the suspension feels tight and quiet over bumps. Included are both original key fobs, the factory floor mats, and a folder of recent maintenance receipts. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
